headline: GNRC Launches Most Powerful Air-Cooled Generator Featuring 28kW Model
summary: Generac unveils a powerful 28kW air-cooled generator, expanding its range to 10-28kW and integrating seamlessly with ecobee and PWRcell for total energy control.

headline: Q3 Earnings Highs And Lows: Generac (NYSE:GNRC) Vs The Rest Of The Renewable Energy Stocks
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q3. Today, we are looking at renewable energy stocks, starting with Generac (NYSE:GNRC).
